^*BBarbara Seagram: ^*N|cp||at|If RHO passes, jump to 2S with this hand — think of this hand as being the dummy for partner’s assumed 4-card spade suit.|mb|2s|
PG| ***** 58 ***** |


nt||
cp|8|AT|^B@2
