^*BBarbara Seagram: ^*N|cp||at|With a very weak hand, you would simply pass, so you can now bid a simple 1S—a free bid—and show your values (8+ points).|MB|1S|
pg| ***** 61 ***** |


cp|8|AT|^B@2

^*BBarbara Seagram: ^*N|cp||at|Let’s stick with this auction and look for various other hands you may hold.|
