NT||cp|8|AT|^B@2
^*BBarbara Seagram: ^*N|cp||at|It doesn’t. You can still cuebid opener’s suit (i.e. bid 2D) to show a strong hand that wants to go to game. After all, 4S, 3NT or even 5C might be the best spot, but you need to consult partner to discover which.|mb|2d|
