nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2
^*BBarbara Seagram: ^*N|cp||at|When you have two suits that you could cuebid|CP|1|AT|^*H^*N|CP||AT|diamonds and hearts here, it is obviously possible to assign different meaning to the two cuebids. As you become more comfortable with complex auctions in which both sides are bidding, you may find that you want to do this.|
